  "title": "Add possibility to clear searchBox value using the clearAllWidget",
  "body": "For now the clearAll widget only allows to clear facet refinements, but not the search query itself. Would be great to have a way that enables it, either:\r\n- by having an new option in the widget configuration, and say true|false\r\n- letting define a hook function that would be called once the user has clicked and in which we could call `search.helper.setQuery('').search()` ",
